Use Case-1
# This use case shows how to run an microservice application in a mixed container and virtual machine environment.
# Will Create kubevirt-hyberconverged object for Openshift Virtualization
# Uses Openshift Gitops for Application 



# Known Problems

- For some reason the servicemeshmemberroll does not always catch the namespace correctly or does not inject istio-proxy into pods.If this happens delete the servicemeshmemberroll in istio-system and allow gitops re-create it.
